{"tid":2512114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"單春迅：「香港人很奇怪」","createTime":"2021-05-01T12:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T12:21:18.000Z","uid":176453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e2868bbf0f7b938b6016d7be12f12bd6609399b2","tid":2512114,"uid":176453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXGsireywdR2cFoZyYtZ5m19L6g7HRHRZF15G36r6s6ua?filename=tYusBzJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtYusBzJ.png&h=c9493fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSrcCfXqopxVN2BSRxYKhMSvkyi2DBJhR9oPivqbTGY33?filename=2qq7BzN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qq7BzN.png&h=789244d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅覺得香港人很奇怪<br />\n<br />\n在英國生活了一段長時間，接受英國教育的Eason，對於香港年青人的心態並不是太了解，不過覺得他們學東西很快。雖然香港曾經是英國殖民地，但Eason覺得這兩個地方的人及文化，簡直有天淵之別。<br />\n「我覺得香港人喜歡空口講多個實際做，通常講到天花龍鳳、興高采烈，但是真真正正付諸實行的卻少之又少。好像香港人可以從各式各樣的媒體取得各方面的知識，但卻不會好好利用這些知識。」對此， Eason感到這很奇怪。"},{"pid":"3e3edd8f39e871b356641a47aafd9ae23d965732","tid":2512114,"uid":248131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:21:18.000Z","msg":"話自己愛國都未夠，直接走去同人cut約<br />\n<br />\n結果咪好似佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}